{"type":null,"faqId":48182,"title":"华为手机，无法更换同一类型账号登录华为穿戴APP，怎么办？","answer":"<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">\n<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" id=\"softwareDescription\" jQuery17104971213742414105=\"16\">\n<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">\n<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" id=\"softwareDescription\" jQuery17106823363138297958=\"16\">\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">荣耀/华为手机账号只需要登录一次，之后都是直接登录，无需重新输入账号。如果用户需要更换同一类型账号登陆，请确认用户登录账号为华为账号，还是第三方应用账号（QQ、微信、微博）。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">l&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果是华为账号，需要在手机设置中退出华为云的登录，具体步骤如下（以荣耀6为例）：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">1、&nbsp; 手机设置-华为云服务并点开</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f80_lpi9x.jpg\" jQuery17106823363138297958=\"22\"><img width=\"267\" height=\"455\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f80_lpi9x.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">2、在最下方点击退出账号</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f81_wabph.jpg\" jQuery17106823363138297958=\"23\"><img width=\"267\" height=\"463\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f81_wabph.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">3、进入注销账户界面，点击确定</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f82_mstu1.jpg\" jQuery17106823363138297958=\"24\"><img width=\"267\" height=\"455\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f82_mstu1.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">4、在输入密码界面，点击忘记密码?</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f83_xv8g9.jpg\" jQuery17106823363138297958=\"25\"><img width=\"267\" height=\"457\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/84f83_xv8g9.jpg\"></a></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">5、之后请按照步骤操作即可。</p>\n如果是第三方（微信、QQ、微博）账号，请更换第三方平台登陆账号，然后再登录华为穿戴APP。 </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3847","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1446428710000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":71,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":12,"times":3,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"k1-g01,荣耀小k,儿童手表,k1,绑定,配对,连接,华为穿戴,app,账号,更换,华为手机,更换账号,同类型辰,拆卸,替换,换,相连,衔接,接连,连结,连合,用户名,third-party application,third part,third party,apps,application,applications,program,programs,application program","avgScore":4.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}